## Connect your data

1. Open Qwery (web or desktop).
2. Add a datasource (PostgreSQL, MySQL, DuckDB, etc.).
3. Use natural language to ask questions.

## Example

Ask: "Show me the top 10 customers by revenue."

Qwery will generate the SQL and return the results.
